<el-table :data="tableData" style="width: 100%">
  <el-table-column type="expand">
    <template slot-scope="props">
      <el-table border style="width: 100%" :data="tableData">
        <el-table-column prop="date" label="序号" width="80" type="index"></el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="date" label="商品名称" width="180">{{ props.row.name }}</el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="name" label="所属店铺" width="180">{{ props.row.shop }}</el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="address" label="商品 ID">{{ props.row.id }}</el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="address" label="店铺 ID">{{ props.row.shopId }}</el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="address" label="商品分类">{{ props.row.category }}</el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="address" label="店铺地址">{{ props.row.address }}</el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="address" label="商品描述">{{ props.row.desc }}</el-table-column>
      </el-table>
    </template>
  </el-table-column>
  <el-table-column label="序号" prop="id" type="index"></el-table-column>
  <el-table-column label="商品 ID" prop="id"></el-table-column>
  <el-table-column label="商品名称" prop="name"></el-table-column>
  <el-table-column label="描述" prop="desc"></el-table-column>
</el-table>
